properties.name: Pediatric and Perinatal Chiropractic Center
properties.description: Pediatric and Perinatal Chiropractic Center is a holistic chiropractic center in Fort Myers. The doctors at this office can serve as primary care provider for both children and their parents. They also have their own whole foods supplements.
properties.why_on_wapf_list: Dr. Brie and her teammates employ holistic and natural practices to encourage health in their patients, and they are generally in line with WAPF principles. They encourage parental freedoms and choice when it comes to vaccines.
